---
title: "constructor (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_validate_addrs: check assetOut != 0 and assetOutReceiver != 0
    q_validate_addrs --> q_revert_zero: assetOut == 0 or assetOutReceiver == 0
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress
    q_validate_addrs --> q_set_min_bid: addresses valid
    q_set_min_bid --> q_set_asset_out: _setMinBidUsdValue(minBidUsdValue)
    q_set_asset_out --> q_set_receiver: _setAssetOut(assetOut)
    q_set_receiver --> q_set_fee_agg: _setAssetOutReceiver(assetOutReceiver)
    q_set_fee_agg --> q_validate_multiplier: _setFeeAggregator(feeAggregator)
    q_validate_multiplier --> q_revert_zero_val: minPriceMultiplier == 0
    q_revert_zero_val --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_validate_multiplier --> q_store_multiplier: minPriceMultiplier > 0
    q_store_multiplier --> q_emit: i_minPriceMultiplier = minPriceMultiplier
    q_emit --> [*]: emit MinPriceMultiplierSet

    note right of q_validate_addrs
        INV-001: assetOut and assetOutReceiver must be non-zero addresses
        INV-002: minPriceMultiplier must be non-zero
    end note
